{"tid":2283074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟議會聽證 駐中代表一談及人權 網絡即時中斷","createTime":"2020-11-12T09:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T04:40:54.000Z","uid":130406,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8b3fa94ac2552fa7d304b7a81dcd67fa1aa468","tid":2283074,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"本週一，歐盟議會就中歐商貿關係舉行了聽證會，但駐華代表回答有關中國人權問題的質詢時，網絡連線突然中斷。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;歐盟議會連線接入的專家是歐盟商會常<span class=\"red\">駐上海</span>的代表伍德克（J&ouml;rg Wuttke）。他擅長同中共官員打交道，但也敢於仗義執言。<strong><span class=\"red\">他談到了中國在氣候保護方面的承諾，以及產權保護等方面的問題。但當他說到'現在來談談人權問題吧&hellip;' 網絡連接突然中斷。此後多次嘗試重新連接都未能成功。</span></strong><br />\n不瞭解中國安全機關運作方式的人，恐怕會認為這只是一次令人煩惱的網絡故障，當時在場的大多數歐盟議員也都認為這只是無線網絡不夠穩定而已。&quot;<br />\n文章作者寫道，作為常駐北京的記者，他深知網絡中斷絕不是偶然事件。因為每逢敏感話題，記者的網絡也都會準時發生&quot;故障&quot;。文章接著寫道：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;習近平領導下的中國，已經不再花費力氣去掩飾打壓言論自由的行為了。但是，中國政府居然會在歐洲議會公開展示真面目，就不能不說是一件頗有諷刺意義的事了。<br />\n週二，一度被噤聲的歐盟商會駐華代表伍德克表示：'我從來沒遇到過這種事情。這也許說明中國當局正變得越來越緊張。不過，在歐洲議員面前暴露這種心態，只能達到適得其反的效果。'<br />\n因為這樣一來，歐洲議員就完全有理由質問：我們真的應該同中國放開了做生意嗎？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.dw.com/zh/%E5%BE%B7%E8%AF%AD%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E8%B0%88%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83-%E5%B0%B1%E6%96%AD%E7%BD%91/a-55567710?fbclid=IwAR34-2JHfqfOSmUUR7aAKEmvH022UYkEYJDFCTriozPYj4-5aNViMk0_Fxk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.dw.com%2Fzh%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%25AF%25AD%25E5%25AA%2592%25E4%25BD%2593%25E8%25B0%2588%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259D%2583-%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%2596%25AD%25E7%25BD%2591%2Fa-55567710%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR34-2JHfqfOSmUUR7aAKEmvH022UYkEYJDFCTriozPYj4-5aNViMk0_Fxk&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BynwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=5045ed69\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.dw.com/zh/%E5%BE%B7%E8%AF%AD%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E8%B0%88%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83-%E5%B0%B1%E6%96%AD%E7%BD%91/a-55567710?fbclid=IwAR34-2JHfqfOSmUUR7aAKEmvH022UYkEYJDFCTriozPYj4-5aNViMk0_Fxk</a>"},{"pid":"e186cdb462f9adaaf8d2357b4cfab1072f209703","tid":2283074,"uid":130406,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:54:34.000Z","msg":"支那依家做到咁露骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直頭面都唔洗畀班歐豬<br />\n歐盟會議？話斷網就斷網"},{"pid":"df3d46c9fdded016f0129494af71b8f332839ab5","tid":2283074,"uid":7369,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"信係遇發性事件嘅人應該去驗腦"},{"pid":"06b5da3af5bc9d7cc30b0ac72036c895d2a9bf94","tid":2283074,"uid":86204,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:55:10.000Z","msg":"我們真的應該同中國放開了做生意嗎？<br />\n人民幣真香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a503b19ea8eb6ff51d73bae66580e054e89be740","tid":2283074,"uid":61207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:55:57.000Z","msg":"人地講我聽唔到咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff26e645d895c9dbad24b7e6fad9bc009077bef","tid":2283074,"uid":103207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"左膠：中斷直播十分合理，要保護人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ef6c19b3e32c6de4bbc9065e3c1bcfdb630b6b","tid":2283074,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:56:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc22fdbee22cde1d5ad001800476e46f5688e25e","tid":2283074,"uid":152476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:57:06.000Z","msg":"自從Biden疑似當選<br />\n中共就唔再扮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea68201087d9a11ec85daf2a4fe919967fe04f9e","tid":2283074,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:57:55.000Z","msg":"係咪用左屌為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07ef968becd0a86d7bdcf89f7bf8a8f619c735a","tid":2283074,"uid":130406,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"分鐘班歐豬都想了解下中国人權狀況<br />\n一cut線就即刻了解更多<br />\n比專家9up更快易明<img src=\"/assets/fa